txt.en: In the depths of Kidzul-kâlah, something evil has taken root. The Maiden of the Gladden has asked for your help in removing the corruption.
Pass the Test of the Maiden
The Maid wishes to test your strength before allowing you passage into the mines of Kidzul-kâlah.
Now that you have passed the Maid's test, it is time to confront the darkness within the mines.
Passed the Test of the Maiden
